  "title": "Aures - Create Style for Refined Storage",
  "description": "The container mod is now in brass color!",
  "body": "Curseforge - https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/create-style-for-refined-storage\n\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/BlackAures1/image_lib/blob/main/small_mods/2023-11-23_13.19.153243333333.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>■ - <strong>Create Style for Refined Storage</strong>&nbsp;is a resourcepack that makes the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/refined-storage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Refined Storage</a> fresher and more copper/brass/medieval/steampunk looking!&nbsp;The main version is <strong>1.19.2 and 1.20 (new version).</strong><br>■ - Compatibility with <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/refined-storage-addons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">RefinedStorageAddons</a>, <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/extrastorage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ExtraStorage</a>, <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cable-tiers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">CableTiers</a>.<br>■ -&nbsp;<strong>Artist:</strong> Black Aures, rafaelveras and nocubeyt</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>📖 Permissions &amp; FAQ</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>You are allowed to include this texturepack in videos as long as download link leads to this curseforge page.</li>\n<li>You can only use this mod as part of your modpack if it is in the Curseforge Ecosystem.</li>\n<li>You are not allowed to reupload this mod to other websites and launchers.</li>\n<li>You cannot use assets/data from this mod in other projects.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/BlackAures1/image_lib/blob/main/small_mods/2023-11-23_13.19.15324333333.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1090/637/213324123213-png.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2016\" height=\"919\"></p>",
